      • getTollAmount

        public double getTollAmount(Id<VehicleType> vehicleType,
                            Link link,
                            double time)
        Gets the toll-amount for vehicleType on Link link at time 'time'.

        In case of RoadPricingScheme.TOLL_TYPE_CORDON the toll amount on a link is equivalent to rps.getLinkCostInfo(...).amount.

        In case of RoadPricingScheme.TOLL_TYPE_DISTANCE the toll amount on a link is equivalent to rps.getLinkCostInfo(...).amount*link.getLength().

        Parameters:
        vehicleType -
        link -
        time -
        Returns:

      • addPricingScheme

        public void addPricingScheme(Id<VehicleType> vehicleTypeId,
                             org.matsim.roadpricing.RoadPricingScheme pricingScheme)
        Adds a RoadPricingScheme for vehicleTypeId.

        Currently, only Cordon and Distance tolls can be calculated.

        In case of RoadPricingScheme.TOLL_TYPE_CORDON the toll amount on a link is equivalent to rps.getLinkCostInfo(...).amount.

        In case of RoadPricingScheme.TOLL_TYPE_DISTANCE the toll amount on a link is equivalent to rps.getLinkCostInfo(...).amount*link.getLength().

        Parameters:
        vehicleTypeId -
        {@link - RoadPricingScheme}
